  "_tier": 3,
  "_notes": "Tier 3 Example: Stripe payment webhook handler. Includes: (1) Signature verification, (2) Timestamp validation, (3) Idempotency handling - duplicate events return cached response, (4) Audit logging for compliance, (5) Proper status codes. Additional Tier 3 requirements not shown: monitoring dashboard, alerting, rate limiting, error trigger with escalation."
